Great! I'd be happy to help you plan your trip from Punta Gorda to Michigan. Based on your preferences and the information provided, here is a suggested itinerary for your week-long trip starting from March 6th to March 12th, 2022, keeping in mind your new budget of $4,400.

Day 1: March 6, 2022 - Punta Gorda, FL to Pellston, MI

* Self-driving from Punta Gorda, FL to Pellston, MI (estimated cost: $122)
Duration: 21 hours 40 mins, distance: 2,457 km

Note: Due to the unavailability of a direct flight from Punta Gorda to Pellston and considering your budget preference, I suggest self-driving. It would be an opportunity for you to enjoy the scenic views along the way. If you prefer flying or require any assistance with booking accommodations, please let me know.

Day 2: March 7, 2022 - Pellston, MI

* Explore Pellston and its local attractions (e.g., Pellston Historical Museum)
* Dine at a local American restaurant, such as The Backdoor Lounge or Legs Inn in nearby Cross Village
* Overnight in Pellston

Day 3: March 8, 2022 - Pellston, MI to Traverse City, MI (Self-driving)

* Self-driving from Pellston, MI to Traverse City, MI (estimated cost: $6)
Duration: 1 hour 49 mins, distance: 137 km

Day 4: March 9, 2022 - Traverse City, MI

* Explore Traverse City and its local attractions (e.g., Sleeping Bear Dunes National Lakeshore)
* Try French cuisine at a local restaurant, such as Amical or The Cook's House
* Overnight in Traverse City

Day 5: March 10, 2022 - Traverse City, MI to Alpena, MI (Self-driving)

* Self-driving from Traverse City, MI to Alpena, MI (estimated cost: $10)
Duration: 2 hours 29 mins, distance: 204 km

Day 6: March 11, 2022 - Alpena, MI

* Explore Alpena and its local attractions (e.g., Thunder Bay National Marine Sanctuary)
* Dine at a local American restaurant, such as The Cabin Restaurant or John A. Lau Saloon & Grill
* Overnight in Alpena

Day 7: March 12, 2022 - Alpena, MI to Punta Gorda, FL (Self-driving)

* Self-driving from Alpena, MI to Punta Gorda, FL (estimated cost: $120)
Duration: 21 hours 39 mins, distance: 2,401 km

Please note that the driving duration and distances are approximate. For a more accurate estimation, you can use online mapping tools like Google Maps. Additionally, I have not included accommodation or activity costs in this itinerary, so please let me know if you would like assistance with those as well.

I hope you find this suggested itinerary helpful for planning your week-long trip from Punta Gorda to Michigan. If you have any questions, need further adjustments, or require additional information, please don't hesitate to ask!
